<div class="review-list">
  
  
      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="1017677">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1017677/" class="title-link">换个角度读历史</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1017677"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/bluebay/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1054921-3.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/bluebay/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">Von</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar30 main-title-rating" title="还行"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2005-12-30"
      class="main-meta">2005-12-30 19:55:47</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_1017677_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  历史并不枯燥，读这本书，你会觉得历史也可以读的津津有味，也可以当成一个个短小的故事来读。 与有些书不同的是，他还为我们分了类，从儒，从道，从权术等多方面解读历史。 还算是不错的一本历史书。

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/1017677/#comments">(1回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">3有用 / 0没用</span>
