  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="1084185">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1084185/" class="title-link">趣味历史，深刻回味</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1084185"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/richard_fan/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1292179-2.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/richard_fan/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">柴米油盐</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2006-10-23"
      class="main-meta">2006-10-23 13:49:58</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_1084185_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  读到这本书的时候大概是一年前了，当时还没有在豆瓣上注册，但是今天还是非常想再次推荐这本书。 宋太祖赵匡胤非常喜欢读书，但不是读死书，而是理论和实际结合，以史以书为鉴，知得失，看未来，我们读历史书的时候也要多从这些方面来考虑和思考。 这本书就给了我很多这样思考...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/1084185/#comments">(1回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">1有用 / 1没用</span>
                  </div>
